| TIP-224 | Extending Thales Council Governance Epoch | Draft | @Red | Extending the following epoch to 6 months| https://discord.com/channels/906484044915687464/1278847893511602218 | 2024-08-19

## Simple Summary

Extending the ninth and subsequent governance epoch to 6 months from 4. 

## Abstract

This TIP proposes extending the Thales governance epoch to 6 months. Previously the council would sit for an epoch of 4 months. 

## Motivation

Decrease voter/nomination fatigue, and the increase stability of the sitting council.

## Specification

Extend the Thales Council governance epoch to 6 months starting with the ninth sitting council. 

7 "Yes" are needed for this to pass as its a meta-governance TIP. 

## Rationale

As Thales mature a longer sitting council will provide more stability between the members and tasks. 
In its infancy the Thales Council would to sit for 6 months and was reduced to 4 months give opportunity to new members, this opportunity isn't loss and we are hoping to see less voter/nomination fatigue. 

